query:
INSERT INTO mailchimp_course_tags (
          tag_name,
          tag_id,
          course_language_group_id,
          marketing_mailing_list_access_token_id
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
        ON CONFLICT (course_language_group_id, tag_name)
        DO UPDATE
        SET
          tag_name = EXCLUDED.tag_name
